\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces bigblue3 (1298 macros, seed=42): the raw diffusion draft (left) piles macros at a corner. Post-processing VSR (middle) spreads them out to achieve $-79\%$ violations but grows wirelength by $18\%$. Intra-sampling VSR (right) retains a compact layout that respects the diffusion backbone's implicit wirelength prior, achieving $-82\%$ violations and $-35\%$ wirelength vs.\ the baseline.\relax }}{11}{figure.caption.33}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:postvsintra}{{5}{11}{bigblue3 (1298 macros, seed=42): the raw diffusion draft (left) piles macros at a corner. Post-processing VSR (middle) spreads them out to achieve $-79\%$ violations but grows wirelength by $18\%$. Intra-sampling VSR (right) retains a compact layout that respects the diffusion backbone's implicit wirelength prior, achieving $-82\%$ violations and $-35\%$ wirelength vs.\ the baseline.\relax }{figure.caption.33}{}}
